Short Description:
------------------

   Star Hammer distributed by HomeBrew Software.  Become a
   Starfighter pilot in this mission-based space combat
   game with MIDI music and digitized sound. Joystick
   support. VGA, 500K RAM required. (v1.0)    <ASP>


Long Description:
-----------------

   Star Hammer distributed by HomeBrew Software.  2268 and
   still the war rages on. Mankind has been at war for 28
   years with the evil race known as the Sloboids. Become
   a Starfighter pilot in this mission-based space combat
   game.  Features full-screen 16 direction scrolling,
   save game, full dynamic Adlib/Soundblaster sound-track,
   digitized speech and action galore.  Joystick supported.
   VGA, 500K RAM required. (v1.0)    <ASP>


Registration Information:
-------------------------

   Registered users get the latest version of the complete Star Hammer
   game along with the printed manual.

   For complete user registration information please refer to the
   ORDER.FRM text file.








